{"tid":660254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵招標引入QR Code入閘","createTime":"2018-05-10T14:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T08:34:24.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1e253d3f1c9804671679158e9a0f7c79dc226e8e","tid":660254,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/220424_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F220424_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5d9b19fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵正在進行招標，擬引入二維碼（QR Code）技術，乘客將來或可以用手機一嘟入閘。有不少網民歡迎新技術，但亦有人質疑掃描二維碼需時，將造成入閘機堵塞的情況。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵的招標文件顯示，計劃引用二維碼付款系統，乘客可以利用二維碼入閘出閘。文件列明，投標者需要是金管局認可的儲值支付工具持牌人或支付卡計劃營運機構，意味八達通卡有限公司、支付寶、微信支付、PayPal等機構，都有資格投標。<br />\n<br />\n不過不少網民對新技術抱懷疑的態度。在「hkitalk」論壇上，不少人擔心會有閘機堵塞的情況，「 除咗恭喜繁忙車站倍加繁忙之外，都唔知講咩好」、「仲嫌繁時不夠煩？scan qr code 慢過nfc 100倍」、「等你地同班自由痕一齊臨入閘先gen code，先o係閘機慢慢塞」。<br />\n<br />\n其實用二維碼入閘已非新鮮事。本月8日，騰訊（700）與深圳地鐵、港鐵旗下的「港鐵（深圳）」合作，推出了「手機掃碼過閘服務」，讓乘客可以於深圳地鐵所有車站上，利用手機二維碼乘車。<br />\n<br />\n深圳地鐵稱，現階段每個車站至少設置了「兩進兩出」 四部掃碼閘機，而車公廟、福田、老街、後海等大站則至少設置了十部掃碼閘機。2018年年內深圳地鐵全網所有閘機將全部支持掃碼服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/港鐵招標引入qr-code入閘/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5qr-code%E5%85%A5%E9%96%98%2F&d=EkiJN8p3Xhrfj6Ct6vZ8nf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=efe8250b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5qr-code%E5%85%A5%E9%96%98%2F&h=d02aebdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/港鐵招標引入qr-code入閘/</a>"},{"pid":"681862e74fb9cea1bb62b85b18bbc114c49d2854","tid":660254,"uid":184153,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:07:00.000Z","msg":"//意味八達通卡有限公司、<strong>支付寶、微信支付</strong>、PayPal等機構，都有資格投標。//<br />\n又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ec4d6bf56da2cb704e6988f81069a9ef2dab08","tid":660254,"uid":86841,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:08:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d5ec16c2a988de8280abb3de5f7cbc96cf08e12","tid":660254,"uid":3117,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"到底有幾弱智先會咁撚做 找部電話出黎仲要開埋個qr code 先入到 普通人拎八達通入左十個你都未入撚到一個 狗鐵為左支那寶可以入香港到底可以去到幾盡"},{"pid":"b83790e5963d2e1cf9044dcb1f6cfebb165dce78","tid":660254,"uid":165213,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:15:49.000Z","msg":"人地係因為八達通唔普及 先要qr code<br />\n屌你好地地有八達通又退步整qr code 真係腦裝屎"},{"pid":"93546b3b695a4e50b44426c514a7e035dc68b872","tid":660254,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:16:50.000Z","msg":"Apply pay屌打..."},{"pid":"5e9fd67f50c59d1510e51d2ce584062b1565b958","tid":660254,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:18:56.000Z","msg":"一定比alipay or wechart 啦, 話晒連子公司都用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf8a2d87c36aaec89a61f6ab30207a9315dcc13","tid":660254,"uid":127988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93546b3b695a4e50b44426c514a7e035dc68b872","tid":660254,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:16:50.000Z","msg":"Apply pay屌打..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"有三叔仲會同apple 合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69088fee59bb05f96eb11e70dfe9c70f089eaae2","tid":660254,"uid":86433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"最尾好有可能比OEPAY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d33417746271f4443b0255a6bd0bcafb60e4f9","tid":660254,"uid":186095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T